# Branch: main. Bumped 2026-05-03 from 217e5fe to land in-progress
# investigation tooling for fix/mario-dies-on-slope:
#   db9f399  v2 stack-op trace + func-watch snapshot + NLR-detector
#            3-shape coverage. CPU_TR_STACK_OP captures every
#            gen-emitted PH*/PL*/PE* push/pull (old_S, new_S, signed
#            delta, mnemonic id) into the main cpu_trace ring; off
#            by default, gated by stack_op_enable / disable / status
